<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>settings — my diary</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: #faf6ef;
            color: #2d2a24;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .page-container {
            max-width: 540px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        }
        .top-bar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e0d4;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .top-bar a {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #a0937d;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.375rem;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }
        .top-bar a:hover {
            color: #2d2a24;
        }
        .page-title {
            font-family: 'Lora', serif;
            font-size: 1.375rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2d2a24;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }
        .page-sub {
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            color: #a0937d;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e8e0d4;
            border-radius: 0.75rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }
        .card-title {
            font-family: 'Lora', serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2d2a24;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        }
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        }
        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #8B6914;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
        }
        .form-group input {
            width: 100%;
            background: #faf6ef;
            border: 1px solid #e8e0d4;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.75rem;
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
            color: #2d2a24;
            outline: none;
            transition: border-color 0.2s;
        }
        .form-group input:focus {
            border-color: #8B6914;
            background: #ffffff;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.375rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 0.625rem 1.25rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: #2d2a24;
            color: #faf6ef;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: #1a1814;
        }
        .btn-ghost {
            background: transparent;
            color: #a0937d;
            border: 1px solid #e8e0d4;
        }
        .btn-ghost:hover {
            background: #f0ebe1;
            color: #2d2a24;
        }
        .msg {
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            padding: 0.625rem 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .msg-error {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            color: #b91c1c;
        }
        .msg-success {
            background: #f0fdf4;
            border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
            color: #15803d;
        }
        .divider {
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid #e8e0d4;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
        }
        .info-text {
            font-size: 0.8125rem;
            color: #a0937d;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .info-text strong {
            color: #6b5e4e;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
   <body>
    <div class="page-container">
        <div class="top-bar">
            <a href="/dashboard">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"/>
                </svg>
                back to diary
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="page-title">Settings</div>
        <div class="page-sub">Manage your account and security</div>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-title">Change password</div>
            <% if(error) { %>
                <div class="msg msg-error"><%= error %></div>
            <% } %>
            <% if(success) { %>
                <div class="msg msg-success"><%= success %></div>
            <% } %>

            <form action="/settings/password" method="POST">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="currentPassword">Current password</label>
                    <input type="password" name="currentPassword" id="currentPassword" placeholder="enter your current password" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="newPassword">New password</label>
                    <input type="password" name="newPassword" id="newPassword" placeholder="choose a new password" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="confirmPassword">Confirm new password</label>
                    <input type="password" name="confirmPassword" id="confirmPassword" placeholder="re-enter new password" required>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Update password</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        <hr class="divider">

        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-title">Diary lock password</div>
            <p style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:#a0937d;margin-bottom:1.25rem;line-height:1.5;">
                This is the password you enter every time you open the diary. 
                Stored separately in <code style="background:#f0ebe1;padding:0.125rem 0.375rem;border-radius:0.25rem;font-size:0.75rem;">.diary_password</code>.
            </p>
            <form action="/settings/diary-password" method="POST">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="currentDiaryPassword">Current diary password</label>
                    <input type="password" name="currentDiaryPassword" id="currentDiaryPassword" placeholder="enter current diary password" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="newDiaryPassword">New diary password</label>
                    <input type="password" name="newDiaryPassword" id="newDiaryPassword" placeholder="enter new diary password" required>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Update diary password</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        <hr class="divider">

        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-title">About your diary</div>
            <div class="info-text">
                <p><strong>Session:</strong> Your session expires when you close your browser.</p>
                <p style="margin-top:0.5rem;"><strong>Privacy:</strong> Your entries are private and only accessible with your password.</p>
                <p style="margin-top:0.5rem;"><strong>Data:</strong> All your diary entries are stored securely.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>